oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.cluster.kmeans

Class EuclideanDistanceCriterionFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.cluster.kmeans.EuclideanDistanceCriterionFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CriterionFunction

    public class EuclideanDistanceCriterionFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements CriterionFunction
    A CriterionFunction implementation based on the uclidian distance between the last two cluster centers. The function will converge when the euclidean distance between the cluster centers of two consecutive iterations is equal less than the configuration parameter KMeans.CONF_CRIT_FUN_TERMINATION_VALUE
    Author:
    hsaucedo
